column2: SELECT u.up_OBSID as [OBSID],     &&& + cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,    p.PSFMag_i  FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID  ORDER BY x.up_id
